The paper deals with image reconstruction and manipulation, specifically in the context of single image super resolution. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper focuses on texture loss and texture constraining methods, which are relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also employs deep learning techniques, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
